<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="M" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Maw" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Maw,</orth> stomach; applied to animals: <bibl n="shak. ven 602" default="NO" valid="yes">Ven. 602</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mac 3.4.73" default="NO" valid="yes">Mcb. III, 4, 73</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mac 4.1.23" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 1, 23</bibl>. to human beings: <bibl n="shak. mm 3.2.23" default="NO" valid="yes">Meas. III, 2, 23</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. err 1.2.66" default="NO" valid="yes">Err. I, 2, 66</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. jn 5.7.37" default="NO" valid="yes">John V, 7, 37</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h5 2.1.52" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 II, 1, 52</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tim 3.4.52" default="NO" valid="yes">Tim. III, 4, 52</bibl>. Metaphorically: <emph>thou detestable m.</emph> (the grave) <bibl n="shak. rom 5.3.45" default="NO" valid="yes">Rom. V, 3, 45</bibl>.
